          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Over the age of 18 - cytolysis and/or cholestasis WITH prothrombin time less than 50% or greater than 1.5 INR - signed informed consent by the patient or trusted person - without chronic underlying liver disease - cause of acute liver failure not identified at admission - non-participation in a therapeutic study may alter the patient's prognosis"
          },
